# Core Salesforce Development Rules

## Project Context
This is a Salesforce Apex development project following enterprise best practices.

## Code Standards
- All Apex classes must have corresponding test classes
- Test coverage must be >95%
- Use TestDataFactory for reusable test data
- Follow naming conventions: TestDataFactory, HelloWorldTest

